        <h1>Attention Mechanisms in Deep Learning: A Comprehensive Survey</h1>
        
        <div class="authors">
            <span>Chen, Wei, Rodriguez, Maria, Kumar, Ananya, Thompson, James, Nakamura, Yuki, Schmidt, Hans-Peter, O'Brien, Fiona, Singh, Priya, Williams, David, Kim, Soo-Min, Andersen, Erik, Patel, Raj, Murphy, Grace, Fitzgerald, Thomas, Johannsen, Lars, Aziz, Omar, Russo, Giuseppe, Okonkwo, Chidi, Kowalski, Tomasz</span>
        </div>
        
